Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:05.09,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:06.35,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:07.99,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Let's not be hasty here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.54,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:55.59,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.30,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,He said he stopped the \Ncalamity 15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.30,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he claims,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,though he apparently doesn't \Nremember any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember Mr. Matsunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.49,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. We were in the same club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:19.79,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did he ever talk about how he stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:25.33,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't recall ever hearing \Nanything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You went on a class trip
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,during summer break that year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:30.92,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:36.32,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't seem like a good \Nidea to stay confined at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened on that trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.50,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure something happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.32,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.00,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.99,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no help, I know. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:53.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:58.53,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, so there's \Nno need to push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:03.57,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mr. Matsunaga went on the trip, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.04,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.25,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything seem strange about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.00,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess all we can do is ask him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:23.22,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll run it by Matsu for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.04,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to talk to \Nhim, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.28,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.15,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:38.07,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.52,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's all that stuff for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.24,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I stocked up on supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.08,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.00,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? You don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.55,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Just a little carsi—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.26,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,He tries too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.94,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, too, Akazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.30,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.31,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ride in this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.05,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yours doesn't look like it can handle four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:16.94,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.47,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,This car runs better than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.32,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,That was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.92,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.91,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Teshigawara, you're in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.03,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:30.13,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao, since you get carsick, you're up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.04,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.87,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:56.60,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,So Mr. Matsunaga won't be coming \Nback to Yomiyama for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.22,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I spoke to his mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.78,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,and she said he's living at the \Nresort hotel where he works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.75,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}City of Yomiyama \NPlease Come Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.00,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sanami Town
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.48,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out of Yomiyama \Nwithout any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.66,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.95,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.54,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.55,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.35,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, if you're gonna drive that \Nslow, get out of the fast lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.94,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't judge a book by its cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.44,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, I think you're \Npretty easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.29,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Please, describe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Strong and dependable?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.18,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, am I that macho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.98,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,and you've got a strong \Nsense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:36.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.75,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to say, \N"That's not what I meant."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:44.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the tone? So annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.85,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta pay you back now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:56.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're the head \Nof countermeasures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How is it decided who gets that role?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.52,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, they're appointed \Nby the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.16,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a popular job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, you could say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.77,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,they're responsible for \Nthe lives of the entire class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.65,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, were you appointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.70,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I nominated myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.68,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:18.09,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe no one else actually \Nbelieved in the calamity,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.62,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:24.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow such a \Nsenseless phenomenon to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:28.08,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.06,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.64,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,They said Matsunaga was \Nsuddenly called to a reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:54.64,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I left my cell phone number,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.46,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,so he should call me when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.75,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,No point in sitting around waiting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.99,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:08.42,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're outside Yomiyama, \Nthe calamity shouldn't affect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.64,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.60,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,We are near the ocean, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.31,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.20,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't bring my trunks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.54,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,You can get some at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.76,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,They don't cost much. \NI'll buy you a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.19,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not swimming, I won't, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:35.11,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought this \Nmight happen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.26,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that seemed \Nlike a lot of luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:52.71,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a seaside resort, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.01,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention we're outside Yomiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.75,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And it's summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.22,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be too depressing to \Nsit at home the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.26,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to spread our wings a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.02,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.73,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,The sea in summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.30,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.52,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.37,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.34,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.23,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.01,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.89,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set, dunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:19.72,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is your family's summer house nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.57,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:23.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What does your dad do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.24,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.34,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,He's rarely in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.98,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we put on \Nthese little family acts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.36,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,on the rare occasions when he comes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:38.02,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,We may be a family, \Nbut we aren't really connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.72,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:45.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if we find out who \Nthe dead person is after this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:49.68,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,would making them nonexistent \Nstop the calamity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:52.85,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.98,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been triggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.01,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's too late to try \Nto balance everything out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:03.83,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did they connect?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.77,0:12:05.78,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.55,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting every now and \Nthen can't be so bad, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.79,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.43,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone up for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:33.56,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:37.06,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.55,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go back to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.80,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with something \Nfrom a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.08,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,There are also seaside shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:45.61,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.77,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,We're at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:50.20,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,How could we not make the \Nmost of the outdoor life?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You want to cook here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.17,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd get it, Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.38,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,How are we supposed to \Ndo that without any tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.60,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the bases covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:03.04,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this flawless setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.51,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.95,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,This is what was in that huge bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.06,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.93,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,With what ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.56,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Local fare, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.66,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.69,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,With all the stuff you \Nbrought, I should've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.29,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.61,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Local fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.61,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Mochizuki! You brought \Nthe fishing gear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.37,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.15,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then let's see who can \Nround up the most ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do we get anything for \Nwinning or losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.30,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,The loser has to make the food,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.24,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,and the winner gets to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:40.13,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.55,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.48,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:50.30,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,First off, on the Head of \NCountermeasures Team will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.26,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:52.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.73,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Naka— Actually, we'll pass on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.26,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,And me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:59.02,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Now, on the Nonexistent Team will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.06,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:00.90,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.01,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Mochizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.69,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.54,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't exist {\i1}over here{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:07.70,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:12.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So we're competing based \Non the fish we catch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.58,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you find anything \Nbesides fish, it counts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:17.49,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's sea lettuce. It tastes awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's red algae. \NYou can't eat it on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.02,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.68,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.56,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.10,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:03.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kelp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.25,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to catch {\i1}fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.25,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.00,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.65,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Get it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.90,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was going to eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.44,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Octopuses don't eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.75,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll bite if you \Npoke at them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:41.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.38,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've got a big one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.60,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's pulling pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:49.82,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.36,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's your big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.81,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,At least it's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:00.43,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.56,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I've got one this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.34,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.21,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing that on \Npurpose, aren't yo—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:13.24,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:20.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,A sea cucumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.67,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually impressed \Nyou caught one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.15,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it just got caught on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.27,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You creep! Useless jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.67,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:32.49,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,A pufferfish, an octopus, \Nand a starfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:35.35,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,This is kelp, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.88,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,And a sea cucumber, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.92,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,What's in this shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.89,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,A hermit crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.37,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.27,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,This battle ends in a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:53.11,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I picked up some meat and vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.99,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,so let's all eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.36,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:06.25,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Freshly-caught really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.77,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how I love that crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:16.17,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,So delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:23.33,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely can't eat these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.61,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.75,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.63,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I tried calling your cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.04,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Is the battery dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:45.94,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:48.29,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.59,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Careless as ever, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.38,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you found us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.27,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't hard to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:58.53,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,This is the closest beach to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.51,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.76,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,But, wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.15,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Girls sure do change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.59,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be a shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.78,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed quite a bit, yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.53,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Into an old geezer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.53,0:18:12.52,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.99,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 15 years, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.96,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Technically, it's only been 14 years \Nsince our graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.04,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.27,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,That makes us around 30, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.00,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:29.41,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.48,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Have I seen you somewhere recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.51,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.78,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.88,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably a different girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.98,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:44.34,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe it was at Kentarou \Nor Natsuko's memorial services?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:48.35,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,No, I only went to the funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:49.77,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:53.36,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it's been \N15 years since they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.42,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Who're the kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:59.54,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,This year's class 3 students.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.23,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:04.62,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,They're here about what \Nhappened 15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:09.80,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can only remember bits and \Npieces of that summer, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.29,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu, I heard that you \Nstopped the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:18.05,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoka at Inoya asked \Nme about that, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.56,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:24.94,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall the class \Ntrip we took that summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.43,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.77,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,An accident happened \Non that trip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:31.85,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:32.80,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.98,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa, the head of countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:36.49,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:39.49,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, \NI don't remember much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:43.32,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone died \Non the mountain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.24,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,My memory's hazy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.58,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind \Nof accident it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:53.54,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did the accident happen before you \Nvisited the shrine, or after?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.24,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it was before,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.88,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,maybe a blessing from the \Nshrine stopped the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.19,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.72,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,But, something tells \Nme it was a run-down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.39,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,abandoned-looking shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.59,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Right, the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.93,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we went to the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:14.87,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,We all joined hands and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:18.28,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I just can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:20.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mr. Matsunaga,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:24.11,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,didn't you leave something behind, \Nas a clue for the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.20,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, I said that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.14,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:35.38,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is that I felt this \Nurgent need to tell them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.50,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You can't remember what about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:42.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't remember what you \Nleft behind, or where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:45.26,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Like if it was a note, or something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:51.11,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't paper... It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.19,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:56.26,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think I used something...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.09,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! It's at the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:01.49,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I took something to the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.70,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.58,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.15,Default,Nakao,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.13,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,How far out are you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.85,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.32,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,The hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.49,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, quit messing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.46,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.44,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:44.60,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:47.68,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I protected them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:51.67,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,I left it for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:53.99,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,...in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.83,0:24:39.94,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Body paint.
